    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"necessary and positive force\" you're talking about is exactly what people call \"woke\" when they think it's going too far. if the movement's very method of achieving change is seen by a huge portion of the population as harmful or exclusionary, why can't you just say it's a divisive/controversial thing instead of framing it as something fundamentally \"positive\"?",
